          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The produced beryllium ions were separated according to",
                "their magnetic rigidity and their energy loss in an",
                "achromatic aluminum degrader placed at the dispersive",
                "central focal plane of the FRS. For the production of",
                "Be-12, a degrader with a thickness of 5  g/cm**2 was",
                "used, and for the production of Be-14 the thickness of",
                "the degrader was 1 g/cm**2."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "IOCH",
                "MWPC",
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                " IKAR-the hydrogen-filled ionization chamber-The main",
                "part of the experimental setup was the active target",
                "IKAR, which was used simultaneously as a target and a",
                "detector for the recoil protons.",
                "The detector IKAR consists of six independent identical",
                "modules."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " A primary beam of 18O, accelerated in the UNILAC and",
                "SIS accelerators, interacted with an 8 g/cm**2 Be-",
                "target placed at the entrance of the FRagment Separator"
              ]
            }
          ],
